{"tid":500204,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣轉涼了 下周一低至11度","createTime":"2017-12-15T14:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T06:15:22.000Z","uid":29320,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d72c69196be9f5b4798e5e5e09308d3a4b9afdd","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/222237_222eaca2bef4998ec63bf7daf458bdc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F222237_222eaca2bef4998ec63bf7daf458bdc0.jpg&h=15122385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一道冷鋒會在今晚抵達廣東沿岸地區，天文台預料明日天氣顯著轉涼，與其相關的強烈冬季季候風會在星期日及隨後數天持續影響華南，區內天氣寒冷、乾燥及風勢頗大。下周一氣溫低至11度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2670371/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2670371%2F&d=%2FRaH1x5qWITByysv8wuJn10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=70029717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2670371/</a>"},{"pid":"661fa3f6d934043a0c08f6a3b86b9be6076e4da7","tid":500204,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b52af94a41d097ad50a61b9f6e801e844b73143b","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛耕田，馬食穀，<br />\n老竇賺錢仔享福。<br />\n象行田，馬行日，<br />\n過河卒仔不退縮；<br />\n兵殺敵，將閃縮，</blockquote><br />\n做咩9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0298d19b2f3086c381070c0bd4c05daa56a1d490","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"f0af19ff726c34aaa587242fc7fd33664731e8fb","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"好想攬住個鬼妹 幫佢取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4add31ca321a53091885c4fef2f89bc439a1d2c","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"好凍"},{"pid":"3317a002631a3b0eaca2adb081880c44b87aa7e9","tid":500204,"uid":79870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9038d36255456d892c474e34b468be76b011c49d","tid":500204,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"右邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9ad128e42f5062a46646da0e57395f02cd356b","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"我一定揀中間"},{"pid":"904b425f1f7d6850209f9c90ff200de85ce4140b","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:25:46.000Z","msg":"大家凍嗎？"},{"pid":"f6eb665f803e08f0c0703ea2b7349ca77124d4d0","tid":500204,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"好圖好圖"},{"pid":"18171fac3d7765cd140a5ebb4794954d591f9a54","tid":500204,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6eb665f803e08f0c0703ea2b7349ca77124d4d0","tid":500204,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"好圖好圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:49:23.000Z","msg":"小心冷親呀"},{"pid":"6aa3960ea97f7ea52c7cac031bf5e68dbe04dd16","tid":500204,"uid":146588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"